\&    [\-\-arch ARCHITECTURE] [\-\-attach ISOFILE]
\&
\&
\&
\& virt\-builder \-l|\-\-list [\-\-long] [\-\-list\-format short|long|json]
\&
\& virt\-builder \-\-notes версія\-ОС
\&
