.el .IP "\f(CWhttps_proxy\fR" 4
.IX Item "https_proxy"
.ie n .IP """no_proxy""" 4
.el .IP "\f(CWno_proxy\fR" 4
.IX Item "no_proxy"
.PD
Set the proxy for downloads.  These environment variables (and more)  are
actually interpreted by \fIcurl\fR\|(1), not virt-builder.
.ie n .IP """HOME""" 4
.el .IP "\f(CWHOME\fR" 4
